headline: IVZ Q3 Deep Dive: Broad-Based Growth, Strategic Streamlining, and Global Expansion Drive Results
summary: Asset management firm Invesco (NYSE:IVZ) reported Q3 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 48.5% year on year to $1.64 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.61 per share was 39% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
